                            <ul>
                                <li>A platform to network across different groups</li>
                                <li>Turn PITP into an annual meet-up of housing groups</li>
                                [1 hour, 5pm – 6pm, Main Tent]   
                            </ul>
                    </ol>
                    <p class="text-muted3">[Ends: 6pm]</p>
                    <p class="text-muted3">Speakers, Workshops and Panels to be confirmed in due course. </p>
                    <p class="text-muted3">Additional Elements running concurrently:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><em class="text-muted3">Stage/ Speaker’s Corner: </em>Have a speaker’s corner/ soap box in festival for people to talk about housing; small acoustic stage with co-op members performing</li>
                        <li><em class="text-muted3">People's Court: </em>invite developer/ councilor and put them on trial, with audience as jury.</li>
                        <li><em class="text-muted3">Housing Information Stall</em>, along with main sponsor stalls (Hexagon HA, Sanford HC)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
